sparkline._queryString:
select ID, Location, Batch,
  `$"," vs' string New_Alerts,
  `$"," vs' string Temperature,
  `$"," vs' string Flow,
  `$"," vs' string Conductivity,
  `$"," vs' string Ozone,
  `$"," vs' string Combo_Change from CIPSHistData where Plant = `Tokyo

pivot._queryString: select quoteCount:count i,quoteSpread:10000*avg (ask-bid),quoteSize:avg (bidSize+askSize)%2 by hour:`$string time.hh,minute:`$string 10 xbar time.minute, sym,src from dfxQuote

zoom._queryString: select Date, Open from SharePrice where Share = `GOOG

radar._queryString:
{[s] s: flip select PE_Ratio_TTM, Forward_PE: ForwardPE, PEG_Ratio, Price_Sales_TTM: PriceSales_TTM, Price_Book_MRQ: PriceBook_MRQ from .stocks.fundamentals where s = sym 

    }

    }
